561
00:37:56.958 --> 00:37:57.788
KB.

562
00:37:58.500 --> 00:38:00.250
Ah. <i>the</i> KB Molapo.

563
00:38:00.333 --> 00:38:01.503
Wade.

564
00:38:01.583 --> 00:38:03.633
