565
00:38:03.708 --> 00:38:05.828
Whatever. Let's go get fucked up. man.

566
00:38:09.958 --> 00:38:13.288
Don't mind him. Um. we were
just about to get something to eat.

567
00:38:13.375 --> 00:38:14.995
-Do you wanna come?
-Yeah. sure.

568
00:38:18.291 --> 00:38:20.631
