-No.

569
00:38:20.708 --> 00:38:22.078
What's happening here?

570
00:38:24.041 --> 00:38:25.331
Is this even packing?

571
00:38:27.083 --> 00:38:30.293
You know.
most young people would be ecstatic

572
00:38:30.375 --> 00:38:32.125
