573
00:38:33.041 --> 00:38:38.001
I mean. it's a beautiful place
to advance your career prospects.

574
00:38:38.083 --> 00:38:39.923
Right? Okay.

575
00:38:43.958 --> 00:38:44.788
What is it?

576
00:38:45.333 --> 00:38:46.333
Talk to me.

577
00:38:50.083 --> 00:38:53.213
Is there anything that you regret doing.

578
00:38:53.708 --> 00:38:54.788
or not doing?

579
00:38:56.500 --> 00:38:57.830
Sometimes. I…

580
00:38:59.250 --> 00:39:01.420
