584
00:39:08.208 --> 00:39:11.078
We regret not spending
enough time with our loved ones.

585
00:39:11.750 --> 00:39:15.130
you know. creating good memories.
whether good or bad. but…

586
00:39:18.125 --> 00:39:19.875
