591
00:39:47.000 --> 00:39:49.080
Um. and pack better.

592
00:39:55.750 --> 00:39:57.630
Oh. there we go.
Thank you.

593
00:39:59.416 --> 00:40:01.246
Oh. I really like that one.
It's really nice.

594
00:40:01.875 --> 00:40:05.495
Hey. uh. lovebirds. I'm gonna have
