601
00:40:46.250 --> 00:40:50.630
So. um… remember at-- at the matric ball.

602
00:40:51.833 --> 00:40:54.383
my card got full
so I went to go get another one?

603
00:40:54.458 --> 00:40:55.328
Uh-huh.

604
00:40:57.125 --> 00:40:58.205
