-Do you still like him?

612
00:41:24.583 --> 00:41:25.423
No.

613
00:41:27.041 --> 00:41:29.331
No. Wade. I want to be with you.

614
00:41:30.708 --> 00:41:32.328
I-- I think I should go.

615
00:41:32.416 --> 00:41:33.246
Wade…

616
00:41:33.750 --> 00:41:35.460
Yeah. I'm-- I'm gonna go.

617
00:41:35.541 --> 00:41:36.831
Wade. please. just…

618
00:41:37.416 --> 00:41:38.666
