629
00:42:18.416 --> 00:42:20.416
Look. I-- I make a great Zulu-tini.

630
00:42:20.500 --> 00:42:22.250
Uh. speak to the manager.

631
00:42:22.333 --> 00:42:23.213
-Manager?
-Yes.

632
00:42:23.291 --> 00:42:24.711
