652
00:43:29.458 --> 00:43:31.168
Oh. your work's incredible.

653
00:43:32.875 --> 00:43:33.955
You an artist too?

654
00:43:34.791 --> 00:43:37.421
Oh. No.
I'm still in high school.

655
00:43:37.916 --> 00:43:39.626
Ah. I see.

656
00:43:39.708 --> 00:43:40.918
