658
00:43:45.333 --> 00:43:46.673
Anthony Gabisa.

659
00:43:48.041 --> 00:43:49.171
Lovely meeting you.

660
00:43:50.250 --> 00:43:52.630
All the best figuring things out.
Fikile Bhele.

661
