674
00:44:51.125 --> 00:44:54.035
Uh. I'm-- I'm sorry too.

675
00:44:55.166 --> 00:44:57.576
And I like you too. a lot.

676
00:45:01.708 --> 00:45:03.168
Hey. what the hell?

677
00:45:05.000 --> 00:45:06.380
